Load averages typically increase due to excessive utilisation of one of combination of the following system resources:
1. CPU
2. RAM
3. Disk
4. Network

Some of the commands that can be helpful here to find out which resource(s) are under saturation:
1. top
2. free -m
3. vmstat
4. iostat
5. sar
6. dmesg
